notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: T.I., and T.H. conceived and designed the study. T.H., Y.S., A.O. and H.H contributed analytical procedures. T.I. conducted the microscopic and sequencing analyses and analyzed the data. H.A. performed the spectroscopic analysis and analyzed the data. T.I. prepared all figures and tables. T.I. and T.H. wrote the paper and all co-authors edited the manuscript.
